If you change the return type of this method to ClassLoader, then you can add this:
return WildFlySecurityManager.getCurrentContextClassLoaderPrivileged();

And then the test can validate that it returns newOutTccl. That both serves as a sanity check that newOutTccl was in place before the notification handling, and confirms that it got restored.

